<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="768" height="1024" viewBox="0 0 768 1024" role="img" aria-label="The Ballet of Floating Memories">
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="bg" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#7A3E2B" />
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#F8F5EF" />
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>
  <rect width="768" height="1024" fill="url(#bg)" />
  <rect x="48" y="48" width="672" height="928" rx="40" ry="40" fill="#FFFDF9" opacity="0.95" />
  <rect x="88" y="108" width="592" height="360" rx="28" ry="28" fill="#FFFFFF" opacity="0.85" />
  <rect x="88" y="516" width="592" height="340" rx="28" ry="28" fill="#FFFFFF" opacity="0.92" />
  <text x="112" y="170" fill="#7A3E2B" font-family="Georgia, serif" font-size="28" font-weight="700">Mon Livre Magique</text>
  <text x="112" y="228" fill="#111827" font-family="Georgia, serif" font-size="42" font-weight="700">The Ballet of Floating Memories</text>
  <text x="112" y="284" fill="#6B7280" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="22">STORY</text>
  <text x="112" y="360" fill="#374151" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="24">Asset admin par defaut issu du blueprint</text>
  <text x="112" y="416" fill="#6B7280" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18">Magical watercolor masterpiece, child with chestnut bob in sage cardigan reaching toward floating crystal flowers containing tiny luminous memory scenes, golden moss floor, ethereal lighting, premium fantasy storybook illustration</text>
  <text x="112" y="588" fill="#111827" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="24" font-weight="700">Texte template</text>
  <text x="112" y="640" fill="#374151" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="24">In this secret garden, crystal flowers drift above golden moss. Within each translucent petal, tiny scenes come alive: a waltz beneath the gazebo, sugar waffles shared with joy, laughter bursting in the rain. {child_name} holds their breath, wonderstruck.</text>
  <text x="112" y="906" fill="#6B7280" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18">Produit Sylius pilote par book_blueprint_json</text>
</svg>